{"tid":2092122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪得我覺得移民係暫時，目的係令抗爭終極進化，而唔係落地生根永別香港？","createTime":"2020-07-03T05:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T07:16:43.000Z","uid":168267,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"914d48f6f771db4db5bf77a90ce3b0a62a848576","tid":2092122,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:06:14.000Z","msg":"見到移民潮，其實我好興奮<br />\n因為抗爭可以再進化<br />\n因為我知道街頭抗爭嘅力量真係變得好有限<br />\n因為我諗起嘅，係<span style=\"color: red;\">Victor嘅《2019前線革命宣言》</span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家仲記得：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/19uVZkLMrMdpr8ZIeBjkc236oR2U2S3fGZ4QPa5_nmZA/mobilebasic?fbclid=IwAR1tuEifyY3fHrwlAnpb8b6ABJxopIJ_kg1SH8x4-kCVUWiuW5Ie8xXhdPg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F19uVZkLMrMdpr8ZIeBjkc236oR2U2S3fGZ4QPa5_nmZA%2Fmobilebasic%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1tuEifyY3fHrwlAnpb8b6ABJxopIJ_kg1SH8x4-kCVUWiuW5Ie8xXhdPg&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXJ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=f39470a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/19uVZkLMrMdpr8ZIeBjkc236oR2U2S3fGZ4QPa5_nmZA/mobilebasic?fbclid=IwAR1tuEifyY3fHrwlAnpb8b6ABJxopIJ_kg1SH8x4-kCVUWiuW5Ie8xXhdPg</a><br />\n<br />\n但依家無論係支持移民定反對移民，都係集中討論點樣去融入人哋地方<br />\n<strong>反對嘅</strong>：郁啲就話走、都唔係齊上齊落、唔好聚居去到人哋度做蝗蟲<br />\n<strong>支持嘅</strong>：依家唔走將來想走都唔得、邊度樓價平、買車交稅交通咩情況<br />\n正反兩邊個重點都係<span style=\"color: red;\">點樣歸化外國同成為理想嘅移民</span><br />\n<br />\n但呢個移民潮其實令我期待，因為香港人可以真正physically走出國際，而且我好清楚文宣、國際戰線背後，本來就有好多好多唔係香港人，甚至唔係黃皮膚嘅人為香港出心出力，本來呢件事就唔係侷限喺香港，如果幾百萬人都賴死唔捨得走我仲驚<br />\n就算做唔到東印度公司、V小隊口中嘅情況，但起碼離開嘅人唔使開口埋口池袋炸麵、香港倒立先<br />\n<br />\n令我特別擔心嘅係「唔好好似蝗蟲咁聚埋一齊colonize人哋」呢種講法<br />\n因為呢種睇法<span style=\"color: red;\">前設係將移民視為從此bye bye香港條尾</span>，覺得移民並冇包含抗爭，所以聚居唔啱<br />\n其實個人嚟講想你哋至少傾掂佢搵一度地方聚埋一齊，保留香港民族精神，同埋叫做有個基地，我<span style=\"color: red;\">前設係呢個diaspora係暫時</span>，目標係爭取遲早一日會返嚟屬於我哋嘅靚香港<br />\n不過本人愛國愛港唔會走，所以其實have no stake in the discussion<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />純粹個人睇法<br />\n<br />\n而支持離開嘅人無非係想多啲手足避開國安法<br />\n38條就係想令大家去到海外都自我審查，只要你一日仲諗住喺香港未康復嘅情況下返嚟，就算你離開太陽系都唔會敢盡情發聲<br />\n離開嘅人，一係決心一戰到底，唔成功唔罷休<br />\n咁先有機會實現下面呢個承諾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1280/1*DPR_lvPR1iGshGsIb0tUIw.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1280%2F1%2ADPR_lvPR1iGshGsIb0tUIw.jpeg&h=8638de1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n期望今次移民潮係be water嘅香港人再進化去下一階段嘅契機"},{"pid":"c4e8890871c8a0b3704a11c001234d4339a0ef4c","tid":2092122,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe072d06d2522b984e47d0d8af5513b13abda632","tid":2092122,"uid":359483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"至慘嘅係呢批走嘅人大多數都係以自身利益為先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家唔走遲啲走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88c5c1a415047c8c790dcc97ba6ab487941e6cd","tid":2092122,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe072d06d2522b984e47d0d8af5513b13abda632","tid":2092122,"uid":359483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"至慘嘅係呢批走嘅人大多數都係以自身利益為先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家唔走遲啲走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"保自己其實冇問題，殷海光都話要滿足咗最基本嘅需求先會諗點追求真善美<br />\n問題係滿足咗之後有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0123e6a39ed158c689fbce2661316afec78cdecd","tid":2092122,"uid":359483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b88c5c1a415047c8c790dcc97ba6ab487941e6cd","tid":2092122,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe072d06d2522b984e47d0d8af5513b13abda632","tid":2092122,"uid":359483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:12:43.000Z","msg":